These are not really good comparisons - boc/sod/vt weapons are very difficult to get.  All these upgrades are more difficult to obtain than an epic.  Meeles obtain their dps upgrades through weapons, mages, mainly through pets.  Turning in a parchment is not difficult.  Why should meeles have to kill aow/farm st presleeper release/complete the most difficult key quest to get upgrades, while mages simply need to hand in a parchment that drops off tier 1 yard trash ? (there are really very few uber meele weapons that dont require a substantial amount of effort to get...fleshgrinder is a decent one I can think of off the top of my head, but I cant think of too many - especially on the order of boc/sod/etc).<br>
<br>
If the mage epic is going to be obsolete, fine.  But put a greater than epic upgrade(s) on aow/ntov/ssra/vt or something just like meeles get (thats about the level of progression warriors need to reach in order to justify banking red blade generally).<br>
<br>
